data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_5_huecos
data.value: To add a new segment, drag it from the column on the left and drop it on the plan. You can create a new segment by pressing the "New Segment" button.

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_5_sensores
data.value: To add a new sensor, drag it from the column on the left and drop it on the plan. A window will be opened where you can select one of the available sensors of that type in that location (if none appears, you must create it before in the sensors section).

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_5_todo
data.value: To add a new sensor or segment, drag it from the column on the left and drop it on the plan. A window will be opened where you can select one of the available sensors of that type in that location (if none appears, you must create it before in the sensors section). You can create a new segment by pressing the "New Segment" button.

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_7_huecos
data.value: To remove a segment, drag it to the trash bin located in the actions column. To delete selected items or ALL of them if nothing is selected, click on the trash bin icon directly.

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_7_sensores
data.value: To remove a sensor, drag it to the trash bin located in the actions column. To delete selected items or ALL of them if nothing is selected, click on the trash bin icon directly.

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_7_todo
data.value: To remove a sensor or segment, drag it to the trash bin located in the actions column. To delete selected items or ALL of them if nothing is selected, click on the trash bin icon directly.

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_seleccion_huecos
data.value: You can click on a segment icon in the plane to select it, click the "Select all icons" button to select all of them or click the "Deselect all icons" button to deselect all. Once the icons have been selected, they will be shown with the green border in the segments. You can change the position of all the selected icons in the map simultaneously using the W, S, A, D keys (Up, Down, Left and Right respectively).

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_seleccion_sensores
data.value: You can click on a sensor icon in the plane to select it, click the "Select all icons" button to select all of them or click the "Deselect all icons" button to deselect all. Once the icons have been selected, they will be shown with the green border in the green icon of the sensors. You can change the position of all the selected icons in the map simultaneously using the W, S, A, D keys (Up, Down, Left and Right respectively).

data.name: Mensaje_ayuda_seleccion_todo
data.value: You can click on a sensor or segment icon in the plane to select it, click the "Select all icons" button to select all of them or click the "Deselect all icons" button to deselect all. Once the icons have been selected, they will be shown with the green border in the case of the segments, or the green icon in the case of the sensors. You can change the position of all the selected icons in the map simultaneously using the W, S, A, D keys (Up, Down, Left and Right respectively).
